message.text:
Do you like to play music and perform? Are you creative, interested in leading and creating amazing events for all of LundaEkonomerna's members to enjoy? Then becoming Project Leader for the LE Band may be something for you! 

LE Band is the house band of LundaEkonomerna and plays at many of the internal events and seatings that LundaEkonomerna hosts. On a normal year, LE Band plays live at Vinterbalen, Pytten, and several other large events and sittnings.

 Find out more and apply no later than 25th of May at lundaekonomerna.se/get-involved
